\[\nu^{*}=\min_{\pi}\max_{\mathscr{R}\in\mathscr{R}}\sum_{s,x}\widetilde{ \mathcal{R}}(s,x)P(x\mid s)\left(\rho(s)-\pi(x\mid s)\rho_{\bm{\pi}}(s)\right)\] (14)

